HEADWORD: Humic
<hw>Hu"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>humus</ets>
the earth, ground: cf. F. <ets>humique</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
